This Repl is set up as a template for students taking Python for
Everybody to get a copy of the sample code and input files from
from the course web site at www.py4e.com via a replit template.

Python for Everybody (www.py4e.com) is the world's most successful
online programming course.  PY4E is available on Coursera, edX,
and FutureLearn as well as many other sources.  All of its
content, lectures, book, and auto are available free of charge
with a Creative Commons license that allows remixing and re-sharing
of the content under the terms of Share-Alike.

Python for Everybody is part of an overall curriculum by Dr. Charles
R. Severance that you can explore at online.dr-chuck.com
